## ðŸ§  Smart Behavior

* [ ] **Auto-detect Active Client Type**

  * Use sniffing (response headers, login page, etc.) to suggest the appropriate client (qBittorrent, Deluge, etc.).

* [ ] **Multi-client Mode**

